<h2>Bregenz Opera On The Lake</h2>
<p>Sit back and enjoy the spectacle of Mozart’s The Magic Flute being performed in Bregenz, on the world’s largest lake stage as part of the famous ‘Bregenzer Festspiele’ We can arrange tickets as part of our inclusive holiday programmes to Lindau and nearby Lochau but early booking is recommended.</p>
